snippet.textDisplay:
Loving & enjoying Coke Studios from San Francisco. Such excellent talented musicians & incredible vocals. The late Nuzrat Fateh Ali Khan is still the best spiritual qawalli devotional singer. The young ones don't seem to have his devotional spiritual depth which they need to cultivate. 
Thanks Coke Studios for this superb, magnificent amalgamation of some of the best musicians & singers in the Indian subcontinent. Namaskar. So Yum. Sukria.🤲🙏🧡
